<li id="cite_note-FAarticle-39"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-FAarticle_39-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-FAarticle_39-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Official copy (free preview): <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.foreignaffairs.org/19930601faessay5188/samuel-p-huntington/the-clash-of-civilizations.html">The Clash of Civilizations?</a>, <i><a href="Foreign_Affairs" title="Foreign Affairs">Foreign Affairs</a></i>, Summer 1993</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Joireman-40"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Joireman_40-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book">Joireman, Sandra Fullerton (2003). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=cFT4HYDUlh0C&lpg=PA30&ots=TfWqt9ksoi&dq=Samuel%20Huntington%20primordialist&pg=PA30#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false"><i>Nationalism and Political Identity</i></a>. London: Continuum. p.&#160;30. <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/0-8264-6591-9" title="Special:BookSources/0-8264-6591-9">0-8264-6591-9</a><span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=cFT4HYDUlh0C&lpg=PA30&ots=TfWqt9ksoi&dq=Samuel%20Huntington%20primordialist&pg=PA30#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false">http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=cFT4HYDUlh0C&amp;lpg=PA30&amp;ots=TfWqt9ksoi&amp;dq=Samuel%20Huntington%20primordialist&amp;pg=PA30#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false</a></span>.</span></span></li>
</ol>
